		<section id="H58F246AD1ED346E1A1595F6A62A34983" section-type="section-one">
      <enum>1.</enum>
      <header>Short title</header>
      <text display-inline="no-display-inline">This Act may be cited as the
			 <quote>
          <short-title>Northern Border Regional Commission Reauthorization Act of
			 2013</short-title>
        </quote>.</text>
		</section>
    <section id="H2A0FD6F3A1F9482993101CB6277EA5E7">
      <enum>2.</enum>
      <header>Northern Border
			 Regional Commission</header>
			<subsection id="H92BBFEEB7ED04ECB95C3F4E750D5F438">
        <enum>(a)</enum>
        <header>Authorization of
			 appropriations</header>
        <text display-inline="yes-display-inline"><cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="uscode" value="usc/40/15751">Section 15751
			 of title 40, United States Code</cato:entity-ref>, is amendedâ€”</text>
				<paragraph id="H0CB9CAFE2EFA4024B949EA6CA4EE5766">
          <enum>(1)</enum>
          <text>by redesignating
			 <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="uscode" value="usc/40/15751/b">subsection (b)</cato:entity-ref> as <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="uscode" value="usc/40/15751/c" proposed="true">subsection (c)</cato:entity-ref>;</text>
				</paragraph>
        <paragraph id="H6ACE7D7554454CAD845F8B36C9B9BD8B">
          <enum>(2)</enum>
          <text>by inserting after
			 <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="uscode" value="usc/40/15751/a">subsection (a)</cato:entity-ref> the following:</text>
					<quoted-block display-inline="no-display-inline" id="H4EEE9848DFAB42E7804A4BDA97F1D9C1" style="USC">
						<subsection id="H714E9537A0D94201AAE8D245C0C943E2">
              <enum>(b)</enum>
              <header>Northern Border
				Regional Commission</header>
              <text display-inline="yes-display-inline"><cato:entity xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="auth-auth-approp">There is
				authorized to be appropriated to the <cato:entity-ref entity-type="federal-body" value="Northern Border Regional Commission" proposed="true">Northern Border Regional Commission</cato:entity-ref> <cato:property name="purpose">to
				carry out this subtitle</cato:property> <cato:funds-and-year amount="30000000" year="2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018">$30,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2014 through
				2018</cato:funds-and-year>.</cato:entity></text>
						</subsection>
            <after-quoted-block>;
				and</after-quoted-block>
          </quoted-block>
				</paragraph>
        <paragraph id="H9352BB769262489394317254FFD83A69">
          <enum>(3)</enum>
          <text>in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="uscode" value="usc/40/15751/c">subsection (c)</cato:entity-ref>,
			 as so redesignated in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Northern Border Regional Commission Reauthorization Act of 2013/s:2/ss:a/p:1" proposed="true">paragraph (1)</cato:entity-ref> of this subsection, by inserting <quote>by
			 the <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" value="Northern Border Regional Commission" proposed="true">Commission</cato:entity-ref>, if in that fiscal year at least $10,000,000 is made available
			 to the <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="federal-body" value="Northern Border Regional Commission" proposed="true">Commission</cato:entity-ref> under this section</quote> before the period.</text>
				</paragraph>
      </subsection>
